#################
###### OVH ######
#################

IMAPAccount ovh
Host ssl0.ovh.net
User thibault@thb.lt
AuthMechs LOGIN
PassCmd "gopass show ssl0.ovh.net"
SSLType IMAPS

ImapStore ovh-remote
Account ovh

MaildirStore ovh-local
Path ~/.mail/thb.lt/
Inbox ~/.mail/thb.lt/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel ovh
Far :ovh-remote:
Near :ovh-local:
Patterns % INBOX
Patterns * % !Drafts
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync All
Expunge Both
Remove Both # Note that for safety, non-empty mailboxes are never deleted. (manpage)

